<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mountainhome Herald</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/global.css">
    <style>
        #container { max-width: 800px; }
        .categoryStrip { background-color: #ece9d8; padding: 4px 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #003366; }
        .categoryStrip a {
            color: #003366; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 12px;
            padding: 2px 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px;
        }
        .categoryStrip a:hover, .categoryStrip a.active { background-color: #003366; color: #ffffff; }
        .mainCol { float: left; width: 580px; }
        .sidebarCol { float: right; width: 190px; }
        .clearfix::after { content: ""; display: table; clear: both; }
        .featuredBox {
            border: 2px solid #003366; margin: 10px 10px 10px 15px; padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .featuredBox .featuredLabel {
            background-color: #cc0000; color: #ffffff; font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold; padding: 2px 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; display: inline-block;
        }
        .featuredBox h2 { font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 6px 0; }
        .featuredBox p { font-size: 11px; margin: 4px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
        .topStoriesBox { margin: 10px 10px 10px 15px; }
        .topStoriesBox h3 {
            background-color: #003366; color: #ffffff; padding: 4px 8px;
            margin: 0 0 0 0; font-size: 12px;
        }
        .articleCard { border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 6px 8px; }
        .articleCard .cardMeta { color: #666666; font-size: 10px; }
        .articleCard a { color: #003366; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px; }
        .articleCard a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .latestBox { margin: 10px 10px 10px 15px; }
        .latestBox h3 { background-color: #003366; color: #ffffff; padding: 4px 8px; margin: 0; font-size: 12px; }
        .latestBox ul { margin: 0; padding: 4px 0; list-style: none; }
        .latestBox ul li { border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding: 4px 8px; font-size: 11px; }
        .latestBox ul li a { color: #003366; text-decoration: none; }
        .latestBox ul li a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .sidebarBox { border: 1px solid #999999; margin: 10px 15px 10px 5px; }
        .sidebarBox h4 {
            background-color: #cc0000; color: #ffffff; padding: 4px 8px;
            margin: 0; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold;
        }
        .sidebarBox .sidebarContent { padding: 6px 8px; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }
        .sidebarBox .sidebarContent a { color: #003366; font-weight: bold; }
        .breakingItem { border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding: 4px 0; }
        .catCount { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding: 3px 0; }
        .categoryBadge { padding: 1px 5px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
        .cat-Politics { background-color: #bee3f8; color: #2a4365; }
        .cat-Crime    { background-color: #feebc8; color: #744210; }
        .cat-Economy  { background-color: #c6f6d5; color: #22543d; }
        .cat-Culture  { background-color: #bee3f8; color: #2a4365; }
        .cat-Sports   { background-color: #c6f6d5; color: #22543d; }
        .cat-Weather  { background-color: #feebc8; color: #744210; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <div class="headerBar">
            MOUNTAINHOME HERALD
            <span style="float:right; font-size:11px; font-weight:normal;">Edition No. 847 | March 11, 2026</span>
        </div>

        <div class="navBar">
            <a href="/news/">Home</a>
            <a href="/news/articles">Articles</a>
            <a href="/news/about">About</a>
            <a href="/l1/taxes/">ROD Records</a>
        </div>

        <div class="categoryStrip" id="categoryStrip">
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('')" class="active" id="cat-All">All</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Politics')" id="cat-Politics">Politics</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Crime')" id="cat-Crime">Crime</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Economy')" id="cat-Economy">Economy</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Culture')" id="cat-Culture">Culture</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Sports')" id="cat-Sports">Sports</a>
            <a href="javascript:filterCategory('Weather')" id="cat-Weather">Weather</a>
        </div>

        <div class="breadcrumbs">
            <a href="/news/">Home</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pageTitle">Today's Edition &mdash; March 11, 2026</div>

        <div class="clearfix">
            <!-- Main column -->
            <div class="mainCol">
                <!-- Featured story -->
                <div class="featuredBox articleCard" data-category="Politics">
                    <div class="featuredLabel">FEATURED</div>
                    <h2>
                        <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-016')">Surface Relations Act Passes Second Reading</a>
                    </h2>
                    <div class="cardMeta">
                        <span class="categoryBadge cat-Politics">Politics</span>&nbsp;
                        March 11, 2026 &mdash; Urist McReporter
                    </div>
                    <p style="margin-top:6px;">
                        The Arcane Council passed the Surface Relations Normalisation Act on second reading
                        Wednesday by a vote of 6-3, advancing the most comprehensive framework for regulating
                        Mountainhome's dealings with surface nations in nearly four decades. Third reading
                        expected within 30 days.
                    </p>
                    <p><a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-016')">Read full story &raquo;</a></p>
                </div>

                <!-- Top 4 stories -->
                <div class="topStoriesBox">
                    <h3>Top Stories</h3>
                    <div class="articleCard" data-category="Crime">
                        <div class="cardMeta">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Crime">Crime</span>&nbsp;
                            March 11, 2026
                        </div>
                        <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-018')">Z-Level 28 Tavern Brawl Leaves Five Hospitalized</a>
                        <div style="font-size:10px; color:#333; margin-top:3px;">
                            A late-night brawl at the Cracked Anvil tavern on Z-Level 28 left five dwarves requiring treatment at the Fortress Infirmary. Fortress Guard investigating.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="articleCard" data-category="Economy">
                        <div class="cardMeta">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Economy">Economy</span>&nbsp;
                            March 11, 2026
                        </div>
                        <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-019')">Steelthunder Clan Files Injunction Against Koganusan Estates LLC</a>
                        <div style="font-size:10px; color:#333; margin-top:3px;">
                            Emergency injunction sought to halt excavation at Z-Level 35 Eastern Cavern, citing 137-year ancestral mineral claim conflict. Hearing set for Friday.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="articleCard" data-category="Sports">
                        <div class="cardMeta">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Sports">Sports</span>&nbsp;
                            March 11, 2026
                        </div>
                        <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-015')">Fortress Wrestling League Opens Season; Avar Ironhand Defends Championship</a>
                        <div style="font-size:10px; color:#333; margin-top:3px;">
                            Sold-out opening card at the Grand Arena. Ironhand submits challenger Urist Stoneback in the second round to retain Heavyweight title.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="articleCard" data-category="Culture">
                        <div class="cardMeta">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Culture">Culture</span>&nbsp;
                            March 11, 2026
                        </div>
                        <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-017')">Goden Boulderback's Platinum Statue Wins Grand Duke's Medal</a>
                        <div style="font-size:10px; color:#333; margin-top:3px;">
                            Master sculptor Goden Boulderback receives the Grand Duke's Medal for Artistic Excellence for his platinum statue "The Overseer's Burden" in the Grand Hall.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Latest news list -->
                <div class="latestBox">
                    <h3>Latest News</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li data-category="Weather">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Weather">Weather</span>&nbsp;
                            <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-020')">Geomancer's Annual Report: Year 312 Trending 'Exceptionally Stable'</a>
                            <span class="cardMeta"> &mdash; Mar 11</span>
                        </li>
                        <li data-category="Crime">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Crime">Crime</span>&nbsp;
                            <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-013')">Rune-Wire Fraud Ring Dismantled; 12 Arrested</a>
                            <span class="cardMeta"> &mdash; Mar 6</span>
                        </li>
                        <li data-category="Economy">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Economy">Economy</span>&nbsp;
                            <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-014')">Plump Helmet Harvest Forecast Slashed 18% After Cave Mold Infestation</a>
                            <span class="cardMeta"> &mdash; Mar 9</span>
                        </li>
                        <li data-category="Politics">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Politics">Politics</span>&nbsp;
                            <a href="javascript:navigateToArticle('MHH-012')">Arcane Council Debates Mandatory Literacy Rune Testing</a>
                            <span class="cardMeta"> &mdash; Mar 2</span>
                        </li>
                        <li data-category="Culture">
                            <span class="categoryBadge cat-Culture">Culture</span>&nbsp;
