                <div class="sidebarBox">
                    <h4>ABOUT THE HERALD</h4>
                    <div class="sidebarContent">
                        Founded Year 89 by Urist McDwarfquill.
                        The Grand Duchy's independent record of events since the Third Age of Mining.
